name: CellCounter
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cell counter
des: This skill allows the user to operate cell counting software with voice. The software analyze images of cells to count the number of cells in the image. The software can also analyze the morphology of the cells. This skill allows the user to either count the cells and/or analyze their morphology.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
